summary: Another contribution to the Unnecessary series by fredlaus
descriptionHtml:
[size=4][color=#ffd966][b][size=6]Another Fabulous & Unnecessary mod by fredlaus: #[color=#cc0000]5[/color][/size][/b]
[size=4]Why unnecessary mods?
Because they make your game beautiful.
You get more place to live, stack your stuff and house your followers
- and increase your self-esteem dramatically.[size=4] He, he.[/size][/size]
[size=4]---------------------------------------------------------------------[/size][/color]
[/size][color=#b6b6b6][size=3][size=3]22052016:
New version 2.0.1 with minor changes.
[size=4][color=#ffd966][size=4]---------------------------------------------------------------------[/size][/color][/size]
Free Mine Village is located near Riverwood on the opposite side of the river.
[color=#b6b6b6][size=3][size=3]This mod can be used along my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75797/?]TS The Mine[/url].[/size][/size][/color]
You will find the following content:
Freemine Fishery with 3 employees. The employees sleep in the fishery.
Freemine Breeze Bank for the Player only. With a bedroom for the Player.
4 homes, in use by workers in the village.
Freemine Traders in use by Adrianne Freemine.
As allways in my "Unnecessary" series there are several unused doors around.
Ignore them or use them.
This is a resource mod to use freely. It is already ticking for you.[/size]
The FaceGenData is included if you need it.
My other Unnecessary mods:
[size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75776/]Mistwatch Twin Tower
